		{"id":"legend","type":"text","x":680,"y":-480,"width":340,"height":520,"text":"## Legend\n\n🔴 **Plane 1 — Episodic**\nfast, source-first, Qdrant\n\n🟠 **Plane 2 — Curated**\ntopic-first, Obsidian vault = source of truth\n\n🟡 **Plane 3 — Artifacts**\nraw documents + chunk index\n\n🟢 **Bridge — Synthesized Concepts**\nbubble up from reinforcement\n\n🟣 **Core + Lifecycle Engine**\nmaturation · synthesis · promotion\n\n🔵 **Interfaces / Retrieval**\ncanonical API + adapters + ranking\n\nSee [[00-index/reading-tour]].","color":"0"}
